{"tid":1996763,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【P牌一問】高速行中線","createTime":"2020-05-01T07:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T01:01:28.000Z","uid":356264,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"67b9902393c63eba5e786b34b78a7a478a617783","tid":1996763,"uid":356264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實高速行中線有無問題？因為學車教P牌要行左線慢線，但我有幾次就係咁出錯出口行錯路..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以依家多行中線, 但就成日俾我女朋友鬧，迫我行返左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dc3d7a41ddeaba68197ab3eb197a3db3b1da77","tid":1996763,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"冇問題"},{"pid":"bfa3923561af14074a1284827a04010768987eba","tid":1996763,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"有問題"},{"pid":"c467e0fd8c87e2bdc89f01d125a4506d34d19e2e","tid":1996763,"uid":53285,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔好比人慢線快過你 is ok, 如果speed limit 快過你 p 牌上咪行最左"},{"pid":"4af245fc783928d8475181ae77ef6ffac25dcc70","tid":1996763,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"自己睇清楚 左線只去出口就cut返線 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc5fcbaaf35ab9404388608808af8b1cd0ea572","tid":1996763,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"到出口先cut 咪得囉"},{"pid":"215975c1019c896a2d321d778aebd63b5858132d","tid":1996763,"uid":430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"Keep left unless overtake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3158f422ba778a96063cbcc144fdc916e115184","tid":1996763,"uid":67527,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"67b9902393c63eba5e786b34b78a7a478a617783","tid":1996763,"uid":356264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實高速行中線有無問題？因為學車教P牌要行左線慢線，但我有幾次就係咁出錯出口行錯路..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以依家多行中線, 但就成日俾我女朋友鬧，迫我行返左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"你女朋友啱，唔識cut線就唔好揸車"},{"pid":"bc625ced19b8ee5d9762cd1033566fff8e734e90","tid":1996763,"uid":43000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PPvMGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PPvMGn.png&h=4c87165e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7adaf771f0095b5a69c48c748be2532bef0ea763","tid":1996763,"uid":139991,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"日日行屯公，入機場，總有啲P牌係鐘意行70係中線頂住人，行70唔緊要，行慢線啦，頂住哂，搞到啲車要左邊過其實仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔熟路就睇完地圖先開車，再唔係行中線都得，唔該跟返返牌行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7fc569e8035fd071574fccb5402c87b045bfbb","tid":1996763,"uid":67653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGQ66Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGQ66Ke.jpg&h=7714285c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常如果最左線會直接出左出口會有減速行車綫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/02/000737_8c8216a4f15fc6963643b736085edf21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F000737_8c8216a4f15fc6963643b736085edf21.png&h=daec8136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBUvOYW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBUvOYW.png&h=dd01b8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你見到有綫而你又想繼續行大路先cut出一條囉"},{"pid":"6ac4baffb591d2be56317448ce03c8296de70184","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"東廊落東隧一定要行快線添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔通唔落咩<br />\n揸車唔係一成不變嘅"},{"pid":"6d288a3544b3db5db3cfec0c131eb5630b7ee055","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc5fcbaaf35ab9404388608808af8b1cd0ea572","tid":1996763,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"到出口先cut 咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得對P牌嚟講仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時就嚟冇得cut過去又把握唔到機會 一係夾硬嚟 一係喺自己正線停低咗<br />\n利申自己P牌 四線高速多數用二線"},{"pid":"1d8fc039d4cd6ba1e2165218e12f81f2d29df5d0","tid":1996763,"uid":25727,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6ac4baffb591d2be56317448ce03c8296de70184","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"東廊落東隧一定要行快線添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔通唔落咩<br />\n揸車唔係一成不變嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁即係你唔知咩叫快線"},{"pid":"7db96005137cdefb6cc85fbb7c2e273df548b552","tid":1996763,"uid":93807,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ac4baffb591d2be56317448ce03c8296de70184","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"東廊落東隧一定要行快線添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔通唔落咩<br />\n揸車唔係一成不變嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"你到底知唔知乜野叫快線"},{"pid":"cee1bc112db4d29e568d2c1a75ae87c587e263e9","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1d8fc039d4cd6ba1e2165218e12f81f2d29df5d0","tid":1996763,"uid":25727,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6ac4baffb591d2be56317448ce03c8296de70184","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"東廊落東隧一定要行快線添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔通唔落咩<br />\n揸車唔係一成不變嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁即係你唔知咩叫快線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jJXuw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jJXuw5.png&h=1e3dd195&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講緊呢種<br />\n去到尾段出口梗係唔當快線啦 但呢啲預告定嘅算唔算？"},{"pid":"67db815bad41d5cbe643e8e0c9d9aabc8ba35aa7","tid":1996763,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T22:06:17.000Z","msg":"盡早選擇行車線<br />\n無事無幹就靠左<br />\n當你知道/見到左線係出口而你唔係出<br />\n就可以盡早 cut<br />\n除咗東廊落東隧呢個係香港快速公路嘅特例<br />\n繁忙時間嘅<br />\n觀塘道葵涌方向接龍翔道<br />\n太子道東上橋去旺角<br />\n全世界都係喺右線慢慢排隊<br />\n左線暢通<br />\n反而如果你靠左駛<br />\n去到最尾先停低 cut 線<br />\n反而變咗打尖<br />\n有時有啲司機未必老嚟俾你讓<br />\n等多幾架車線有位你入嘅<br />\n但又阻到左線直去車（但都無計，條路係咁）<br />\n就算同樣窩打老道浸會橋面北行入獅隧<br />\n明明兩條線都係入獅隧<br />\n好多人都係靠右<br />\n左線暢通"},{"pid":"8dca3e58a177d3f3fd0359766092cc949fbfb407","tid":1996763,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67b9902393c63eba5e786b34b78a7a478a617783","tid":1996763,"uid":356264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實高速行中線有無問題？因為學車教P牌要行左線慢線，但我有幾次就係咁出錯出口行錯路..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以依家多行中線, 但就成日俾我女朋友鬧，迫我行返左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"除非越過前車，請靠左駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c9d0a1b98d73d8270e2f335899de2d5c1258d3","tid":1996763,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"其實無問題嘅<br />\n但我自己長期行慢線好似仲衰<br />\n日頭車多如果個個去曬慢線匯合位好難出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ea1100501dac50f01cb137670faa89f988acf2","tid":1996763,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"唔撚使理樓上啲人<br />\n跟車速限制行中線都叫頂住人？<br />\n<br />\nP牌的確係行中線最穩陣, 唔使cut黎cut 去<br />\n總之適合車速行中線無人吹得你漲"},{"pid":"b8be1a5916a89ca4e0eccd1b70e574ba4c1696f9","tid":1996763,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"其實p牌爬人頭 超左速點計<br />\n同埋點捉p牌超速"},{"pid":"eae0313f203d95c42bd69a946c82c5026585e5f0","tid":1996763,"uid":228929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cee1bc112db4d29e568d2c1a75ae87c587e263e9","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1d8fc039d4cd6ba1e2165218e12f81f2d29df5d0","tid":1996763,"uid":25727,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6ac4baffb591d2be56317448ce03c8296de70184","tid":1996763,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"東廊落東隧一定要行快線添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔通唔落咩<br />\n揸車唔係一成不變嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁即係你唔知咩叫快線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jJXuw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jJXuw5.png&h=1e3dd195&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講緊呢種<br />\n去到尾段出口梗係唔當快線啦 但呢啲預告定嘅算唔算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"運輸署話為咗前往目的地，係可以行快線的"},{"pid":"6693a4595a879718f6c2e7f0f27e673eb1381c99","tid":1996763,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88ea1100501dac50f01cb137670faa89f988acf2","tid":1996763,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"唔撚使理樓上啲人<br />\n跟車速限制行中線都叫頂住人？<br />\n<br />\nP牌的確係行中線最穩陣, 唔使cut黎cut 去<br />\n總之適合車速行中線無人吹得你漲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"問題正正就係好多時候中線啲車都跟牌行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你行得70唔該縮返入去慢線<br />\n真係有慢車頂住先Cut出嚟爬頭"},{"pid":"e8944e6028d8d2d3b041a97ee65c1d03ff6a9346","tid":1996763,"uid":228929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8be1a5916a89ca4e0eccd1b70e574ba4c1696f9","tid":1996763,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"其實p牌爬人頭 超左速點計<br />\n同埋點捉p牌超速"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"捉P牌超速有幾種情況<br />\n1.警車/老隱捉到你超速<br />\n2.自己中快相<br />\n3.自己中地炮<br />\n<br />\n時速低於70同埋超15內，你都可以交錢了事<br />\n<br />\n如果你高過70，中快相/非即時地炮，最好屋企人有車牌<br />\n<br />\n如果高過70，即時派彩就恭喜你先<br />\n<br />\n其實醒水少少留意有無地炮/警車/老隱，跟牌行無人理你的"},{"pid":"0fdc98fd95456b7d3fa6dec96ecc15185663d37a","tid":1996763,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8be1a5916a89ca4e0eccd1b70e574ba4c1696f9","tid":1996763,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"其實p牌爬人頭 超左速點計<br />\n同埋點捉p牌超速"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"快相機唔識認你係咪P<br />\n跟牌行唔會影你<br />\n基本上都係有真狗行動 (老隱/地炮即時派獎) 你先會中招"}]}